---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';

const pageTitle = 'About This Site';
const pageDescription = 'An overview of the purpose, audience, and publishing standards behind PowerAI Load Test 01 20260522-042729105.';
---

<Base title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <p>Pages</p>
      <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
      <p>{pageDescription}</p>
      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2>What this site covers</h2>
        <p>PowerAI Load Test 01 20260522-042729105 exists to publish launch notes, feature explanations, product updates, support-facing information, and related editorial material.</p>
        <p>It is aimed at people evaluating the product, comparing options, or using the service.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2>How content is selected</h2>
        <p>We prefer clear, practical language and content that helps readers understand the site, its topic, and the surrounding context.</p>
        <p>New pages, revisions, and updates are chosen to keep the site useful even when the brand, team, or business details are still evolving.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2>What appears here over time</h2>
        <p>PowerAI Load Test 01 20260522-042729105 is expected to publish launch notes, feature explanations, product updates, support-facing information, and related editorial material.</p>
        <p>The site can cover introduce the product, explain the value proposition, and publish supporting product information.</p>
        <p>That usually includes product pages, launch notes, support material, and editorial updates that help people evaluate the service.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2>How updates are handled</h2>
        <p>If a page becomes outdated, it can be revised or replaced without changing the underlying purpose of the site.</p>
        <p>Readers should expect the content to evolve as the publication matures, especially once actual brand details, authors, or contact routes are added.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
